WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.520
I'm entering that season of motherhood

00:00:01.521 --> 00:00:03.081
where my daughter is starting to steal my stuff,

00:00:03.082 --> 00:00:04.881
like my jewelry, my makeup,

00:00:04.882 --> 00:00:09.381
my hair supplies. So I'm trying to find things that we can share.

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:11.880
She has blonde hair, I have darker hair.

00:00:11.881 --> 00:00:13.521
So I found these gimme hair ties

00:00:13.522 --> 00:00:15.161
which are really nice cause I can use the dark ones,

00:00:15.162 --> 00:00:16.401
she can use the light ones

00:00:16.402 --> 00:00:17.841
and they don't damage your hair,

00:00:17.842 --> 00:00:19.201
they're really soft, stretchy,

00:00:19.202 --> 00:00:20.721
they don't leave a Mark in the hair

00:00:20.722 --> 00:00:23.401
and they're really easy to use.

00:00:23.402 --> 00:00:27.061
She is just now like learning how to put her hair up in a ponytail

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:30.226
and these are like a perfect for her to use on her own.
